         MACRO ,
&NM      FDLADDR &N,&P=R4,&A=R3,&TEST=
.*   THIS MACRO IS USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH SCBILD/SCLIST SERVICE
.*   TO GET THE LINE AND POINTER ADDRESS OF THE NTH LINE.
.*   NOTE THAT NO VALIDITY CHECKING IS DONE ON THE LINE # PARAMETER
.*
&NM      L     &P,EXW@RENT   ADDRESS OF LIST
         LA    &P,(&N-1)*4(,&P)  POINTER TO LINE
         L     &A,0(,&P)         ADDRESS OF LINE
         AIF   (T'&TEST EQ 'O').MEND
         LA    &A,0(,&A)         CLEAN IT
         LTR   &A,&A             ANY?
         MACPARM &TEST,OP=BZ,OPR=BZR
.MEND    MEND  ,
